commit.message:
move default for STACK_PUSH_CODE to defaults.h

gcc/ChangeLog:

2015-05-20  Trevor Saunders  <tbsaunde+gcc@tbsaunde.org>

	* defaults.h: Add default for STACK_PUSH_CODE.
	* expr.c: Don't redefine STACK_PUSH_CODE.
	* recog.c: Likewise.

From-SVN: r223515
